me":"2017-08-04T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人真係好唔玩得<br />\n又孱弱又要怕呢樣怕嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係好唔玩得<br />\n有條友隊完罐啤<br />\n跑跑下突然間突發性心臟病<br />\n主辦佢點孭呢個責任</blockquote><br />\n400米一圈 一人一圈一啤跑四圈或者四人一圈一啤接力 checkpoint有工作人員睇<br />\n我唔知主辦團體有冇做好基本嘢係報名嗰陣清楚講明有咩風險啦<br />\n(理應就有嘅 就算渣馬都有講啦 更何況佢哋又唔係第一次搞beer run)<br />\n衡量過 同意咗 join咗嘅 有乜事都唔會完全係主辦孭晒飛 參加者自己都需要負番相當責任<br />\n有乜事都主辦孭晒嘅 好多活動都冇人再肯搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋 1600米fun run都唔得就咪撚join啦戔累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493b4785b253142c2998f590adf83d41d7cc0a1a","tid":346962,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"1600米都叫馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3491a54168edacde0665b05e39eac92397a56d8b","tid":346962,"uid":122919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"紅酒馬拉松，飲幾多或飲唔飲係悉隨尊便，但beer run係每400m就要飲一杯，合共要4杯，賽規有d唔同<br />\n以我個人體質來講，beer run真係會頂唔順"},{"pid":"19fe4a30d495385c5df28c7c5fad7d95ce34d2b4","tid":346962,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1600米都叫馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接力嘅仲衰 跑得400米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38c68b540d069d6590de8ed220bc4714506285b","tid":346962,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時搞smoke run?<br />\n擔住支萬寶路跑步啦</blockquote><br />\n以前煙草公司都贊助好多體育賽事<br />\n的確唔係幾好"},{"pid":"aa9b1f618ce58db808e5f40e4bc98a5c547488d1","tid":346962,"uid":3534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人真係好唔輕鬆<br />\n難得有呢啲開心活動都要搵醫生律師黎搞死佢